data.title: Tillamook Oregon Zip Code List
data.meta_description: A list of all the zip codes and maps associated with Tillamook, OR - Tillamook County Oregon City of Tillamook zip code map
data.text: Tillamook, OR is a city located in Tillamook County, Oregon and has a land area of 258.94 square miles (670.65 km2). The water area for the city is 17.53 square miles or 45.40 km2. There is one unique zip code in Tillamook, Oregon and it is 97141. The area code(s) for Tillamook is 503/971.
